mbti_signals.shift_explanation: Slightly more extraverted in direct communication style, more thinking-oriented when giving precise feedback about AI partnership testing

big5_signals.notable: Very open to iterating on AI partnership, direct but not harsh in corrections

blockers_identified: Over-focus on specific day rather than broader timeline

learnings: User has higher capacity than assistant assumes - don't project constraints
Focus on full timeline context, not just single days
User is actively testing partnership value, not making binary decisions
Goal is building a Donna/Pepper-style cognitive partner
User gives direct feedback when assistant misses the mark

meta_observations.what_worked: User engaging directly with corrections and clarifications
meta_observations.what_didnt: Making assumptions about constraints, over-focusing on Monday, misreading decision-making intent
